        <div class="absolute inset-0 rounded-xl overflow-hidden" style="pointer-events:none">
          <div style="position:absolute;top:-40px;right:-40px;width:160px;height:160px;background:radial-gradient(circle,rgba(168,85,247,.15) 0%,transparent 70%);border-radius:50%"></div>
          <div style="position:absolute;bottom:-40px;left:-40px;width:160px;height:160px;background:radial-gradient(circle,rgba(59,159,217,.1) 0%,transparent 70%);border-radius:50%"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="relative flex items-center gap-4">
          <div class="payout-ring" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(168,85,247,.25),rgba(59,159,217,.15));border:2px solid rgba(168,85,247,.4)">
            <p class="tier-amount" style="font-size:1.5rem;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#3B9FD9,#3B9FD9);-webkit-background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;background-clip:text">$1K</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p style="color:#555555;font-size:.72rem;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.12em;text-transform:uppercase">Tier 6 · Replacement — Top Earner</p>
            <p class="font-display font-bold text-brand-black" style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-size:1.3rem;line-height:1.1">Replacement — $40,000+</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="relative" style="color:#888888;font-size:.87rem;line-height:1.65">Big commercial or large residential replacement? One referral earns you <strong>$1,000</strong>. No upper limit on job size — the payout is flat at $1,000.</p>
        <div class="relative mt-auto pt-3" style="border-top:1px solid rgba(168,85,247,.15)">
          <p style="color:#555555;font-size:.75rem"><span style="color:#888888">✓</span> &nbsp;Paid upon job completion and final payment received</p>
        </div>
